    "name": "Oatia Skysage Dedication",
    "prerequisite": "trained in *Occultism*",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "Your study of the stars unlocks supernatural insights and magic. You either become trained in Astronomy Lore or an expert in Occultism.  \n  \nYou learn to cast spontaneous spells and gain the Cast a Spell activity. You gain a spell repertoire with two of the following cantrips of your choice: *detect magic*, *guidance*, *know the way*, or *read aura*. You cast these spells as occult spells as you draw on the stars and night sky. You\u2019re trained in occult spell attack rolls and spell DCs. Your key spellcasting ability for these spells is Intelligence.",
